<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/navbar-elem-hover.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/img-gallery.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" defer></script>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md bg-body-tertiary">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/benutzerHome"><img src="../media/bildbearbeitung.png" alt="Logo" height="50" width="50"></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbar" aria-controls="navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Zeige Navbar">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbar">
                <div class="navbar-nav">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/benutzerHome">Home</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/uploadPage">Upload</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/profil">Profil</a>
                </div>
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/logout"><button class="btn btn-danger">Abmelden</button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <h1>Willkommen auf der Startseite ihrer Benutzeroberfläche</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
           
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <p>In der oberen Navigationsleiste finden Sie die Optionen, die es Ihnen ermöglichen, Bilder hochzuladen und zu bearbeiten. Außerdem können Sie unter der Option "Profil" die Daten Ihres Profils einsehen und verändern.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <h2>Ihre Bilder</h2>
            </div>
    </div>

    <section class="gallery">
        <div class="container">
            <% images.forEach((image, index) => { %>
              <% if (index % 3 === 0) { %>
                <div class="row">
              <% } %>
              <div class="col-4 gy-4">
                <img id="galleryImage" src="<%= image.path %>" class="img-fluid rounded" style="box-shadow: 4px 4px 8px black; width: 100%; height: 300px;" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal" onclick="getImagePath(this)">
              </div>
              <% if (index % 3 === 2 || index === images.length - 1) { %>
                </div>
              <% } %>
            <% }); %>
        </div>


        <!-- Modal -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog  modal-dialog-centered  modal-dialog-scrollable"> <!--modal-sm, modal-lg, modal-xl muessen abhaengig von Bildgroesse gemacht werden.-->
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">Aktion w&auml;hlen</h1>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-auto">
                            <img id="modalImgTarget" src="" alt="Detailansicht" class="img-fluid">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                <form action="/edit" method="POST">
                    <input id="imagepath" type="hidden" name="imagePath" value=""> 
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">Bearbeiten</button>
                </form>
                <button id="download" type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="bildHerunterladen()">Herunterladen</button>
                <form action="/delete" method="POST">
                    <input id="imagepathdelete" type="hidden" name="imagePath" value="">    
                    <button  type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">L&ouml;schen</button>
                </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>





        <!--Footer-->
        <footer class="container mt-5">
            <p class="float-end">
              <a href="#">Zur&uuml;ck nach oben</a>
            </p>
            <p>
              © 2023
            </p>
            <p>
              <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/de/kostenlose-icons/photoshop" title="photoshop Icons">Photoshop Icons erstellt von Smashicons - Flaticon</a>
            </p>
          </footer>
    </section>
    
    



    
</body>
</html>
